snippet.title: One Way Road - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1599490/One_Way_Road/

Assume the role of a Space Fleet Captain and take part in numerous space battles as you travel across the galaxy and fight to save humanity. This cinematic narrative driven action-focused space shooter, will take you on a journey into the near future, and put the destiny of mankind in your hands.
